<b>We've introduced a whole bunch of cards.</b>

23:12.360 --> 23:14.500
<b>I did all the introducing!</b>

23:14.500 --> 23:15.610
<b>You just fooled aro—</b>

23:18.280 --> 23:20.190
<b>Game over.</b>

